      "id": "PopularPost237272",
      "post_content": "Ok question for all where this card's effect is concerned, Q: If this creature blocks a creature with trample does trample damage assign to controller if damage is over the defense of the creature?  \n  \nRule 615.6. If damage that would be dealt is prevented, it never happens.   \nA modified event may occur instead, which may in turn trigger abilities.   \nNote that the modified event may contain instructions that can\u2019t be carried   \nout, in which case the impossible instruction is simply ignored.  \n  \nNow as 702.18. Trample, does not exclusivly state that for this instance, it does state that if damage exceeds creatures defense then assign remaining to controller.",
      "posted_by": "andreagrey",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost237272\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">Ok question for all where this card's effect is concerned, Q: If this creature blocks a creature with trample does trample damage assign to controller if damage is over the defense of the creature?<br/><br/>Rule 615.6. If damage that would be dealt is prevented, it never happens. <br/>A modified event may occur instead, which may in turn trigger abilities. <br/>Note that the modified event may contain instructions that can\u2019t be carried <br/>out, in which case the impossible instruction is simply ignored.<br/><br/>Now as 702.18. Trample, does not exclusivly state that for this instance, it does state that if damage exceeds creatures defense then assign remaining to controller.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '237272'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2286\">andreagrey</span>\r\n                                (4/11/2012 7:03:10 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubCo